#: src/introduction.md:123
msgid ""
"Install the CLI, write a first script, run it, embed it in a twenty-line "
"Rust host. Course coverage: Chapter 2, Chapter 31."
msgstr "CLIのインストール、最初のスクリプトの作成と実行、20行のRustホストへの組み込み。コース対応: 第2章、第31章。"

#: src/introduction.md:124
msgid "[EMBEDDING.md](./EMBEDDING.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/introduction.md:124
msgid "Rust host author"
msgstr "Rustホスト作者"

#: src/introduction.md:124
msgid ""
"The complete host-facing reference: `Vm` construction, native function "
"registration, arena sizing, the call and resume protocol, error recovery, "
"opaque host types, the `Library` trait, signed modules. Course coverage: "
"Part IX (Chapters 31 through 39)."
msgstr "ホスト側の完全なリファレンス: `Vm`の構築、ネイティブ関数の登録、アリーナのサイズ、call/resumeプロトコル、エラー回復、不透明型、`Library`トレイト、署名付きモジュール。コース対応: 第9部(第31〜39章)。"

#: src/introduction.md:125
msgid "[PIANO_ROLL.md](./PIANO_ROLL.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/introduction.md:125
msgid "Song author, host lifter, or host architect"
msgstr "楽曲作者、ホスト持ち上げ者、ホスト設計者"

#: src/introduction.md:125
msgid ""
"The long-form manual for the piano-roll example: composing songs, lifting "
"the host loop into another application, and using the example as an "
"architectural reference for other control-loop domains. Course coverage: "
"Part VIII (Chapters 27 through 30)."
msgstr "ピアノロール例の長文マニュアル: 楽曲の作曲、ホストループを別アプリケーションに持ち上げること、例を他の制御ループ領域への組み込みのアーキテクチャ参照として使うこと。コース対応: 第8部(第27〜30章)。"

#: src/introduction.md:126
msgid "[ROGUE.md](./ROGUE.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/introduction.md:126
msgid "Game author or host architect"
msgstr "ゲーム作者、ホスト設計者"

#: src/introduction.md:126
msgid ""
"The long-form manual for the roguelike example: gameplay rules, the host and "
"multi-script architecture, dungeon generation, the artificial-intelligence "
"archetypes, item effects, and exercises. Not covered by a chapter; pointed "
"to from Chapter 40."
msgstr "ローグライク例の長文マニュアル: ゲームプレイのルール、ホストと多スクリプトのアーキテクチャ、ダンジョン生成、AIアーキタイプ、アイテム効果、演習。章での対応無し。第40章から指し示しています。"

#: src/introduction.md:127
msgid "[WHY_REJECTED.md](./WHY_REJECTED.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/introduction.md:127
msgid "Anyone whose program failed verification"
msgstr "検証で失敗したプログラムを持っている人"

#: src/introduction.md:127
msgid ""
"The full catalogue of verifier rejection messages, mapped to root causes and "
"proposed rewrites. Course coverage: Chapter 19 introduces the three most "
"common rejections; this document is the full list."
msgstr "検証器の却下メッセージの全カタログ、原因と提案される書き換えにマッピング。コース対応: 第19章が最もよくある3つを紹介。このドキュメントが全リストです。"

#: src/introduction.md:128
msgid "[FAQ.md](./FAQ.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/introduction.md:128
msgid "Anyone who hit a surprise"
msgstr "意外な振る舞いに遭遇した人"

#: src/introduction.md:128
msgid ""
"Common rough edges in V0.2.0, including string handling, escape sequences, "
"the immutable-locals constraint, and migration notes from the V0.1.x line."
msgstr "V0.2.0でよくある粗削りな点 — 文字列処理、エスケープシーケンス、ローカル不変性の制約、V0.1.x系からの移行ノート。"

#: src/introduction.md:129
msgid "[COOKBOOK.md](./COOKBOOK.md)"
msgstr ""

#: src/introduction.md:129
msgid "Embedder reaching for a known-good pattern"
msgstr "既知のパターンを手に入れたい組み込み開発者"

#: src/introduction.md:129
msgid ""
"Working recipes for embedding patterns: the data-loader pattern, auto-sizing "
"the arena from a module's WCMU, narrow-runtime type aliasing, signed "
"bytecode distribution, calibrated WCET with a measured cost model. Course "
"coverage: Chapter 39 names the patterns; this document is the recipes."
