"Each monster kind in the bestiary names an artificial-intelligence "
"archetype. The host instantiates one Keleusma virtual machine per archetype. "
"Per monster turn, the host invokes the archetype's virtual machine with the "
"monster's position, the player's position, and a line-of-sight flag, and "
