msgstr "Identify。すべての薬を識別済みとマーク。"

#: src/ROGUE.md:413
msgid "Enchant weapon. Advance the equipped weapon tier by `status_arg`."
msgstr "Enchant weapon。装備武器ティアを `status_arg` だけ進める。"

#: src/ROGUE.md:414
